{"tid":2067734,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 行會通過調升退休公務員長糧2.9%　涉款逾7億元料15萬人受惠","createTime":"2020-06-17T07:57:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-17T08:25:05.000Z","uid":2547,"like":6,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"9aa5ab94d98e6ace4bb1074746523d9a9b29c066","tid":2067734,"uid":2547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T07:57:40.000Z","msg":"公務員事務局今（17日）宣布，因應通脹調升，行政會議本月9日通過2020年公務員退休金和遺屬撫恤金增加2.9%，估計約15萬名領取人受惠，庫房則須在2020-21年度額外支付7.58億港元。調升金額於今年4月1日生效，有關決定後日（19日）刊憲後，本月24日須提交立法會作先訂立後審議。<br />\n該局指出，去年4月1日至今年3月31日期間，本港平均每月甲類消費物價指數，較之前12個月上升2.9%，將為退休金及孤寡撫恤金作同步增幅，預計在2020至21年度預算中預留的一般儲備，將足以應付有關額外開支。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />華員會眾退休會員: 全力支持現職公務員凍薪 同舟共濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a72ccb8996f9b6300f7a57b4b2934fe38b2319d","tid":2067734,"uid":259901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T07:58:34.000Z","msg":"獅子山精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1103d978d79eb71615ce4e4a06ab8b6e1f58a7a","tid":2067734,"uid":155818,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T07:58:47.000Z","msg":"笑鳩死<br />\n班奶共既公墓狗凍薪<br />\n舊既公務員長糧加薪<br />\n細蚊仔真係細蚊仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67478232587ce1619138535ce996d5c0889fbc5f","tid":2067734,"uid":53062,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T07:59:03.000Z","msg":"現職冇得加，退休有<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n何志平可能都有份"},{"pid":"18b5200e7cc4090a112885d24b19b98aa87b2d68","tid":2067734,"uid":34252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T08:01:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/CivilSecrets/posts/969363276826123\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FCivilSecrets%2Fposts%2F969363276826123&d=3WJ6yD1ie6